Oliva Mapping Hand Function Imaging Neuroscience 2025


Data includes:

- Anatomical brain-extracted T1w image
- Functional brain data for Force Matching task
- Anatomical defaced T2w spinal cord image
- Functional spinal cord data for Force Matching task


